beer.beer_description:
Blacker than Norwegian metal and smoother than the floors at the Royal Caledonian Curling Club, Horn Swatter is an American Stout that will keep you coming back for more. 

This beer is rich and roasty with loads of dark chocolate and coffee flavours. Finished with a pants load of citrusy, fruity American hops, Horn Swatter is a fitting tribute to Ol’ Pa Brooks and the style of beer that would leave him happier than any other.
